snippet.title: Touhou 東方邪星章 ~ The Last Comer (Danmakufu) - Lunatic 1cc
snippet.description:
Last Comer is one of the newest products in the fully-fledged Touhou fangame department. 

The gimmick might seem a bit familiar to some people, however it's a bit different. 

The stars that fall from the sky fill your trance meter and different stars have different values. Once the meter is full you automatically get a trance, you cannot activate it manually. 
During trance the normal yellow stars will change into high-value blue stars. These are worth millions of points.  
This of course means that you'll have to do some star juggling if you want to activate trances at opportune times. Dodging stars is exceptionally difficult as they have a gigantic hitbox.

As far as I can tell is the slowdown during the final boss nonspells intentional. I don't know why the hud explodes at the end though. 
Also dat bomb glitch at the first death. 

Download:
http://th-jss.cocolog-nifty.com/blog/
